WikiJuice is a Django-based wiki application that allows users to create, read, edit, and delete articles written in 
Markdown.

Features:
Create, edit, and delete wiki articles
Markdown support for article content
Safe Markdown rendering (XSS protection)
Search functionality
Custom 404 error page
Sidebar navigation layout
Input validation and error handling
Recent article detection
Clean UI with responsive layout

To get started:
Clone my github repo:

git clone https://github.com/FueledByOros/Wiki-Crud-Project.git
cd wikijuice

Install Everything you need:

pip install -r requirements.txt

Make Migrations:

python manage.py migrate

Run The App:

python manage.py rumserver --insecure

Visit:

http://127.0.0.1:8000/home